== Lisitsin Gambit ==
Black logically accepted White's gambit and is now attacking White's f3-knight. By far the best move to save it is [[/3. Ng5|3. Ng5]]. On d4 or e5 it can be kicked by pawns, on h4 it does nothing (as long as Black is wary of a Qh5 check) but on g5 it forces Black to defend her e4-pawn.
